Detailed Description

cvmx_ipd_hold_ptr_fifo_ctl

IPD_HOLD_PTR_FIFO_CTL = IPD's Holding Pointer FIFO Control

Allows reading of the Page-Pointers stored in the IPD's Holding Fifo.
